2.0
===
  * Build native code for all available ABIs, copy the binary corresponding to
    the device ABI from assets.
  * Use shared preferences to hold gogoc configuration, then generate
    gogoc.conf from there.
  * Added status notification.
  * Revamped UI.
  * Add a background service to auto-reconnect/disconnect according to current
    network status.
  * Add an option to auto-connect on device startup.
  * New icons generated from SVG.

